'''Indian Premier League''' ('''IPL''') waa horyaal [[cricket]]-ka ragga ah, oo ay ku tartamayaan toban kooxood oo ka kooban toban magaalo oo Hindiya ah. Horyaalka waxaa aasaasay Guddiga Xakamaynta Cricket-ka Hindiya sanadkii 2007.

IPL waa horyaalka cricket-ka loogu daawashada badan yahay aduunka waxaana sanadkan 2014 uu galay kaalinta lixaad marka la isku celceliyo dhamaan horyaalada ciyaaraha. Sanadkii 2010, IPL waxay noqotay dhacdadii ugu horeysay ee ciyaaraha aduunka ee si toos ah loo tabiyo [[Youtube|YouTube]]. Qiimaha sumadda IPL ee 2019 wuxuu ahaa 6.3 US dollar. Xiligii 2015 IPL waxa uu ku biiriyay US$150 million [[Wax soo saarka gudaha|GDP]] ee dhaqaalaha Hindiya.

Waxaa jiray afar iyo toban xilli tartanka IPL. Kuwa hadda haysta horyaalka IPL waa [[Chennai Super Kings]], iyagoo ku guuleystay xilli ciyaareedka 2021

